description:
FoodMicroTeam (FMT) is addressed to the agri-food companies that produce beverages and fermented foods (wine, sparkling wine, beer, leavened bakery products, sausages, cheeses), and that are interested in enhancing the quality of their products. FMT will allow food companies to transfer the Research & Development area to a group of experts able to solve process problems, to innovate processes and products or improve existing ones. The services are: 
�	Process optimization; 
�	Problem solving in food processes; 
�	Product or process innovation; 
�	FoodMicroBank: characterization and conservation of microbial strains isolated from different production processes in order to obtain starter cultures; 
�	Microbiological and chemical analysis of foods.
